{"tid":2256313,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"歎韓牛激嬲黑粉　希澈＠SJ遭辱罵：去自殺吧","createTime":"2020-10-24T08:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T10:55:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4388875c2ddf401996ab95fe67fd0eae7e197010","tid":2256313,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201024/photo/bkn-20201024122247942-1024_00862_001_01b.jpg?20201024131005\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201024%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201024122247942-1024_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20201024131005&h=5ff7511d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓團Super Junior（SJ）的37歲成員金希澈於上月獲委任為某韓牛推廣活動的宣傳大使，故他最近頻頻在社交網上傳大擦韓牛的照片及視頻，沒料到卻惹來黑粉的攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n他今日凌晨在限時動態晒出黑粉給他的私訊，內容如下：「是在炫耀自己有錢，可以一個人這樣吃韓牛嗎？」該網民夾雜着粗口辱罵金希澈，還多次嗌金希澈：「你去自殺吧！自私的人，粉絲連交通費都冇，都仲要慳錢買專輯，Oppa就喺度食韓牛炫耀，都唔諗吓點樣回饋畀粉絲，你如果冇呢張臉，都唔知可以做乜！」而金希澈除了在截圖上打上「我唔會去自殺囉！」還將採取法律行動起訴該網民！"},{"pid":"7eea7b2a366d4c2ada644ea5569d11c00aedc864","tid":2256313,"uid":272819,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"視你老母頻"},{"pid":"716d614d32fa26992fd8966ca5b7a561eff51ce1","tid":2256313,"uid":1086,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T09:00:14.000Z","msg":"又告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33b140e2681a2a02f993e0e68292f67dbc9071f","tid":2256313,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T09:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5224/5224887.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5224%2F5224887.jpg&h=4faf5f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5224/5224888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5224%2F5224888.jpg&h=968f4d9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71be9c7b6aec7